title: M.O.G - Hold My Hand
seo_description: This song is an electrifying worship song, that can catapult you to any realms of the spirit. When you listen to it, you become more connected and attuned to the Father and be filled with the power of worship.
description:
<!--StartFragment-->

This song is an electrifying worship song, that can catapult you to any realms of the spirit.\
\
When you listen to it, you become more connected and attuned to the Father and be filled with the power of worship.
